    <scopecontent id="aspace_9eb0bc36029e862e82f2a4ad40f78f01">
      <head>Collection Overview</head>
      <p>The Charlotte Taft papers contain materials documenting her history as an abortion care
        counselor and activist. The collection chiefly consists of collected newspaper clippings and
        articles documenting struggles for various aspects of reproductive justice. It also contains
        brochures from women's healh care and abortion providers.</p>
    </scopecontent>
